{"tid":1106570,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"原來真係有長生不老既生物","createTime":"2019-04-14T15:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T22:31:41.000Z","uid":137088,"like":424,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"54bed2376969b2e105800a3f6529f9125095f441","tid":1106570,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"燈塔水母<br />\n<br />\n  這種水母物種或許是世界上唯一真正發現不老泉的動物。因為它有能力從一個成熟的成年階段轉變成一個不成熟的息肉階段然後再變回來，或許它的壽命並不受大自然的限製。因為它們能夠忽視死亡，所以個體的數量正在不斷激增。<br />\n<br />\n從理論上說，牠們毫無壽命限制，可以隨心所欲地「返老還童」，完全 anti-aging，難怪成為地球上的長壽冠軍！<img src=\"https://www.am1470.com/data/activities/3865_734390_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am1470.com%2Fdata%2Factivities%2F3865_734390_2.jpg&h=394db345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n燈塔水母，燈塔水母不但能無性繁殖，而且能無視死亡，所以數量也是在不斷的增加，牠們就是「長生不老，永生不滅」的最成功典範。"},{"pid":"b06e2589ba73a4cc112fd8f8f8ec8525c92ee4dd","tid":1106570,"uid":26106,"like":5,"dislike":50,"score":-45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T15:56:36.000Z","msg":"水熊都係啦"},{"pid":"377ed46fc24be6e27cebe21a992d70ab179d6b84","tid":1106570,"uid":120772,"like":503,"dislike":5,"score":498,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"唔好俾中國人知 因間以為食左長壽 即刻絕種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e86484fffa7c25de8b379ec4893560fd54cb17","tid":1106570,"uid":138713,"like":4,"dislike":35,"score":-31,"quote":{"pid":"377ed46fc24be6e27cebe21a992d70ab179d6b84","tid":1106570,"uid":120772,"like":503,"dislike":5,"score":498,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"唔好俾中國人知 因間以為食左長壽 即刻絕種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:42:44.000Z","msg":"快宣揚!"},{"pid":"9b3a0efc3338d14fabcbcb359e810031f80c41ee","tid":1106570,"uid":108467,"like":93,"dislike":3,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"供一世樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33dff36050bae9c6f40bb60ef9e452c12cd9d79