000Z","msg":"source ?"},{"pid":"df5346a0d0eadd28e2f958975738c2c64d90625f","tid":1106570,"uid":37869,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:43:24.000Z","msg":"其實呢隻生物喺細胞層面係點運作<br />\n正常生物的細胞分裂一定次數之後就會衰老而死？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>海佛烈克極限（英語：Hayflick limit）[註 1]，又稱海佛烈克現象（Hayflick phenomenon），指的是一個正常的人類細胞群體，在細胞分裂停止前所能分裂的次數限制。經驗證據（英語：Empirical evidence）顯示，每個細胞的DNA所相連接的端粒，在每次新的細胞分裂後會略微縮減，直至縮減至一個極限長度為止[2][3]。</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/海佛烈克極限\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%B5%B7%E4%BD%9B%E7%83%88%E5%85%8B%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=e7403e4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/海佛烈克極限</a>"},{"pid":"01111b3661a751e4071c3971097418678145711e","tid":1106570,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df5346a0d0eadd28e2f958975738c2c64d90625f","tid":1106570,"uid":37869,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:43:24.000Z","msg":"其實呢隻生物喺細胞層面係點運作<br />\n正常生物的細胞分裂一定次數之後就會衰老而死？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>海佛烈克極限（英語：Hayflick limit）[註 1]，又稱海佛烈克現象（Hayflick phenomenon），指的是一個正常的人類細胞群體，在細胞分裂停止前所能分裂的次數限制。經驗證據（英語：Empirical evidence）顯示，每個細胞的DNA所相連接的端粒，在每次新的細胞分裂後會略微縮減，直至縮減至一個極限長度為止[2][3]。</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/海佛烈克極限\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%B5%B7%E4%BD%9B%E7%83%88%E5%85%8B%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=e7403e4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/海佛烈克極限</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T19:19:12.000Z","msg":"telomere係會變短，但係會有telomerase去加長返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee21cf15aa0eac9d0990cf81a36f771d5c5be47","tid":1106570,"uid":133525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T19:42:56.000Z","msg":"龍蝦都係"},{"pid":"67dd8ad7ed02ac519c1ce5a70478b238e0f4f