d":"01111b3661a751e4071c3971097418678145711e","tid":1106570,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df5346a0d0eadd28e2f958975738c2c64d90625f","tid":1106570,"uid":37869,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:43:24.000Z","msg":"其實呢隻生物喺細胞層面係點運作<br />\n正常生物的細胞分裂一定次數之後就會衰老而死？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>海佛烈克極限（英語：Hayflick limit）[註 1]，又稱海佛烈克現象（Hayflick phenomenon），指的是一個正常的人類細胞群體，在細胞分裂停止前所能分裂的次數限制。經驗證據（英語：Empirical evidence）顯示，每個細胞的DNA所相連接的端粒，在每次新的細胞分裂後會略微縮減，直至縮減至一個極限長度為止[2][3]。</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/海佛烈克極限\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%B5%B7%E4%BD%9B%E7%83%88%E5%85%8B%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=e7403e4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/海佛烈克極限</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T19:19:12.000Z","msg":"telomere係會變短，但係會有telomerase去加長返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T01:59:56.000Z","msg":"個中文名幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fd63c8bed0188cd496390bfc7cc637c1e42da4","tid":1106570,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5227f0581cd635b2cd729915c6d51f9aa9e7b592","tid":1106570,"uid":141261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:11:28.000Z","msg":"荒木飛呂彦表示笑而不語"},{"pid":"f2cbd5f2ea5cb19ceafee5886769b035a434314f","tid":1106570,"uid":94819,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:28:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81f337188a4616ca637a75c0d731211f8ca3301b","tid":1106570,"uid":206083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"02cfb75f4a1694660ac32f4bfd13e7f964ed4f44","tid":1106570,"uid":199957,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"c5a032136a58a349d53713a002d092